/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-run-008-planner.log:2079:/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/refined/chain-03.md:53:- Action: screen immediately for prior-art overlap with Waleffe-type triad analysis, helical decimation, shell-model intuition, and same-helicity favorable-sector lore.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-run-008-planner.log:2260:/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/judgments/chain-03.md:19:This is a strong criticism. Exact coupled identities are cheap compared with the real burden, which is to show that some coupled quantity survives sign restoration, localization, and ordinary inequality losses without collapsing back to energy-only control. The attack is also correct that the Tao comparator was too underspecified and too easy to backfill from a favorable decomposition.
/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/runtime/logs/codex-patlas-beyond-de-giorgi-run-008-planner.log:2261:/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-007/judgments/chain-03.md:24:The attack is correct that this is the decisive step and the original chain did not operationalize the threshold sharply enough. A promoted mechanism must do more than narrate favorable polarized sectors. It must identify how a joint energy-helicity feature reduces one named bad term or excludes one named bad transfer pattern in a quantitatively relevant portion of the full nonlinear burden.
